results.name: Index of appearance of 2*n in A336957, or -1 if 2*n never appears.
comment: It is a strong conjecture that 2*n appears in A336957 for all odd n, and it is known that 2^i does not appear for i>1.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Sep 09 2020
